            "chapterTitle": "Prohibition of attributing wrong Fatherhood",
            "urn": 1626030,
            "body": "<p>Sa'd bin Abu Waqqas (May Allah be pleased with him) said: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"He who (falsely) attributes his fatherhood to anyone besides his real father, knowing that he is not his father, will be forbidden to enter Jannah.\"<br/><br/><b>[Al-Bukhari and Muslim]</b>.</p>",
            "grades": []
